                    <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Meeting SOX and PCI-DSS requirements in the cloud</p>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Multi-layer security architecture</li>
                        <li>Continuous compliance monitoring</li>
                        <li>Automated audit trail generation</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Result:</strong> 100% compliance audit success</p>
