                <div class="challenge-box">
                    <h3>Challenge 2: Application Dependencies</h3>
                    <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Complex interdependencies between legacy applications</p>
                    <p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Detailed dependency mapping</li>
                        <li>Phased migration approach</li>
                        <li>Parallel running during transition</li>
